c=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688050/extras/04056c6be522893df5fee86f9bf44859.avif?t=1754573516\" width=454 height=264 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bring Photos to Life</h2>A picture says a thousand words. Animate them and say a thousand more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688050/extras/7cc6534a9a22bca67855dba2732bd7d3.avif?t=1754573516\" width=324 height=324 /></span></h2></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Breathtaking Blends</h2>Produce compositions of unmatched variety with an unrivaled range of blending modes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1688050/extras/6c177350d82f795808c3f4c412561762.avif?t=1754573516\" width=324 height=324 /></span></h2></ul>",
